-- Micex-RTS Looking for Candidate for President, Vedomosti Says
-- B y   J a k e   R u d n i t s k y
-- 2012-05-17T04:43:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-17/micex-rts-looking-for-candidate-for-president-vedomosti-says.html
The board of  Russia ’s Micex-RTS
exchange will meet on Monday to discuss three candidates to
eventually replace President Ruben Aganbegyan after a year,
Vedomosti  reported , citing an unidentified board member.  The candidates for the post are First Deputy President
Alexander Afanasyev, former MFK Bank chairman Alexander Popov
and member of VTB Capital’s management committee Vladimir
Solokov, the Moscow-based newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jake Rudnitsky in Moscow at 
 jrudnitsky@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Brad Cook at 
 bcook7@bloomberg.net  